$$\log_{16} (r+16) = \frac{5}{4}=\Leftrightarrow 16^\frac{5}{5} =r+16=\Leftrightarrow 256^\frac{1}{4} =r+16=\Leftrightarrow r+16=4^4^\frac{1}{4}=\Leftrightarrow r+16=4\Leftrightarrow r=-12 $$</think>
<answer> \fbox{$r=-12$} </answer>

